  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK775">
<l>viḻittakaṇ vēlkoṇ ṭeṟiya vaḻittimaippi</l>
<l>yoṭṭaṉṟō vaṉka ṇavarkku</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Is it not a defeat to the valiant to wink and destroy their ferocious look when a lance in cast at them (by their foe) ?</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
